title: Ranking the 8 remaining playoff quarterbacks with Danny Kanell (Football 1/9)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Danny Kanell to rank the remaining 8 quarterbacks in the NFL postseason. The guys attempt to balance recent play and previous playoff performances to decide who they would want leading their team if you had to win just 1 game.
